00:29:29.200 --> 00:29:30.079
No tolerance.

00:29:31.279 --> 00:29:32.720
No freedom of worship.

00:29:33.759 --> 00:29:36.640
Only narrow minded bones.

00:29:37.839 --> 00:29:39.759
And oppressed people.

00:29:40.400 --> 00:29:41.759
Do you understand that?

00:30:17.019 --> 00:30:27.009
Holy, you must inserve him.

00:30:27.970 --> 00:30:29.410
The way he wants us to.

00:30:31.009 --> 00:30:32.769
And only that way.

00:30:36.450 --> 00:30:38.930
You my son can become a mighty man.

00:30:39.890 --> 00:30:41.089
With Jehovah's help.

