00:30:51.549 --> 00:30:53.710
Even the good people, even the good sufferers.

00:30:55.549 --> 00:30:56.430
What if you're wrong?

00:30:58.109 --> 00:31:01.069
Isn't it better to offer the other sacrifices too?

00:31:03.069 --> 00:31:03.869
Just in case.

